{"arkId":"cl010114333","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010114333","modified ":"2025-10-31","title":"La bataille sur le plateau, de la tenture de L\u0027Histoire de Scipion","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"La bataille sur le plateau, de la tenture de L\u0027Histoire de Scipion"},{"type":"Autre titre","value":"Bataille sur le plateau de Baecula, de la tenture de L\u0027Histoire de Scipion"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XIV (1643-1715) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1689 - 1690","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1689,"endYear":1690,"imprecision":"","text":"Fin du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Giulio Romano (Giulio Pippi, dit aussi Jules Romain)","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"D\u0027apr\u00e8s","dates":[{"date":"1546","place":"Mantoue","type":"date de mort"},{"date":"1492 ou 1499","place":"Rome ?","type":"date de naissance"}],"creatorRole":"Dessinateur","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q215305"},{"label":"Bonnemer, Fran\u00e7ois","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"D\u0027apr\u00e8s","dates":[{"date":"1689","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"},{"date":"1638","place":"Falaise","type":"date de naissance"}],"creatorRole":"Peintre ; Cartonnier","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q3084032"},{"label":"Manufacture des Gobelins","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1662","place":"Paris","type":"date de naissance"}],"creatorRole":"Atelier de tissage","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q732312"},{"label":"De La Croix, Jean","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Atelier de tissage","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 5388","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"panneau","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Cette bataille se livre sur une montagne escarp\u00e9e que l\u0027arm\u00e9e romaine escalade. Au premier plan, au milieu, deux cavaliers au galop. A droite, d\u0027autres cavaliers et les \u00e9tendards romains.\r\nDans la bordure du bas, six enfants nus, debout ou couch\u00e9s; au milieu, l\u0027un d\u0027eux joue du flageolet, l\u0027autre lient la musique. Dans le bas de la bordure de droite, un enfant verse dans un vase le vin d\u0027une outre.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"446","displayDimension":"446 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"446","displayDimension":"446 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"648","displayDimension":"648 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"649","displayDimension":"649 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Technique : tapisserie = tapisserie sur m\u00e9tier (techniques textile) (Cha\u00eene en laine : 9 fils\/cm - Trames en laine : 20 duites\/cm - Trames en soie : 16 duites\/cm)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laine (chaines et trames)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : soie (trames)","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],